Uses of Package
Entities

  • Packages that use Entities 
    Package Description
    Entities
    Provides all the entities (Models in MVC) and objects involved in client data handling
    Utilities
    Provides generic methods used for many purposes: GUI altering, date-time conversions, etc...
    client
    The Client Package provides all the client connection classes, and communication handling
    controllers
    Provides all the controllers (MVC) of the GUI views involved in the client
